	    * PIN_LED --> LED_PIN
	    * PIN_I2C_SDA --> I2C_PIN_SDA
	    * PIN_I2C_SCL --> I2C_PIN_SCL
	    * DISPLAY_FLAG_4LINES --> DISPLAY_MODE
